item.title: Change ip
item.dc:creator: @Danny068 Danny068
item.description:
@Danny068 wrote:

Right what you do is go to www.no-ip.com. On the site in top left corner click Sign-up now. Add in your details and once you’ve created an account it should come up with a page and a tollbar on the left. Click Add on the left. Another page should come up, fill in the details like Host Name and choose the .no-ip.biz bit. On the ip-Adress bit type in the adress show in the top left coner were it says ‘Logged In As’. Then clikc create host. If you do not understand, i would recommend Mod Thaharok’s guide as it has pictures too.
